---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Caston McDonald" description="About Caston McDonald.">
  <section class="container prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Applied AI, consulting, and systems engineering.</h1>
    <p>
      I am Caston McDonald, an Applied AI Engineer/Consultant and Systems
      Engineering Student. I am interested in building AI systems that are useful
      in real workflows, understandable to the people using them, and shaped by
      the constraints of the environments they live in.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is my home base for reflection and documentation. My X feed
      captures the fastest layer of what I am thinking about, while the blog and
      project pages give the best ideas more structure over time.
    </p>
    <p>
      Current areas of interest include AI-assisted automation, workflow design,
      systems thinking, engineering tradeoffs, and turning early experiments into
      durable tools.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
